Description:
GOLDEN OPPORTUNITY NOT TO BE MISSED!
Enviably situated in the coveted Metro Village Estate, the immediate appeal of this modern residence is more than matched by the spacious interiors that brilliantly showcase the home's allure with a contemporary floor plan. Looked after as a loving family home deserves to be, this immaculate haven has an inviting Open Plan Living with ample kitchen cabinets and pantries, a separate dining area and spacious second living area.
The Master bedroom is carefully tucked away on the upper floor with a extra-large Walk in Robe and an Ensuite with his and hers sinks to ensure maximum privacy. Upper floor also presents 3 good sized bedrooms with BIRs, separate toilet and main bathroom featuring a bathtub.
A remote controlled double garage and a private courtyard is ideal for families. A delightful surprise package, it also includes ducted heating throughout the home, split system and much more!.
Desirably situated opposite the Dandenong Station, within a short walking distance to the retail precinct like Dandenong Plaza and Market, local businesses, pre schools, primary schools, high schools and an abundance of multicultural eateries. Commuting to the city is made easy with Eastlink and Princes Highway close by and Public Transport is within reach.
For further information on how you can make all these yours, please come down to the Open Home or feel free to contact us to take you through privately
Call Ben Jusufi or Burak Gul today for further information!

Description:
First Home, Family Home or Fantastic Investment
Whether you are looking to move in and nest or simply invest and rest, this beautifully presented family home is a winning choice! Central to both Hemmings Park and Greaves Reserve, walking distance to Dandenong West Primary School, Dandenong High School and the fantastic amenities of Dandenong CBD as well as being close to Dandenong Train Station, Eastlink, Princes Highway and the Monash Freeway, convenience and easy living are close at hand.
Light, airy and renovated throughout, the lovely interiors include a large living room and a spacious open plan kitchen, meals and family area with stylish timber look flooring. The trendy kitchen comprises of a 5-burner gas cooktop, underbench oven, soft close drawers and white cabinetry that is accented with black trims and complemented by stone benches that seamlessly continue up as the splashback.
Accommodations begin with a master suite at the front of the home which enjoys a walk in robe and a fully tiled ensuite with large shower. Towards the rear are two additional bedrooms with built in robes, a central family bathroom, separate WC and laundry. Further features of the home include a wall heater, reverse cycle air conditioner, LED downlights and mirrored robe doors.
Set on a block of approximately 457m2, the outdoor spaces provides a patio for outdoor dining, grassed area for kids and pets, a garden shed for handy additional storage space and a double garage for secure off-street parking.
Ready to move straight in and appealing to first home buyers, families and investors, this wonderful family home is certain to be a crowd favourite.
Be sure to inspect without delay and avoid missing out!

Description:
Young, Modern and Convenient!
This modern 2 bedroom villa unit is perfect for couples looking for low maintenance living in a central convenient location. Offering spacious living throughout the large fully carpeted lounge area leads through to separate dining space and modern kitchen with gas cooking.
The villa features ducted heating and cooling ensuring year round comfort. Main bedroom with walk in robe and ensuite style access to main bathroom. Additionally, the unit features separate toilet and laundry room. Bedroom 2 features large built in robes allowing adequate storage.

Located within easy distance to Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong Market, train station, buses and schools, this easy to maintain villa makes the perfect first home or investment.

Description:
Privacy perfection - Stunning 3 bed villa!
In-room Auction Wed 18th September @ 6.30pm
Venue: Sandown Regency Motor Inn - 477 Princes Hwy Noble Park
Hard to find, young and modern 3 bedroom villa unit with large spacious living areas and complemented by gorgeous outdoor entertaining space.
A retirees dream where downsizing doesn't mean giving up all you love like large rooms, gardening and privacy. Only 2 units on the block, this villa is tucked behind with a driveway leading to a double brick garage under roof line with remote door plus separate storage room.
Stunning timber floors throughout with a floor plan that flows with ease. Glass entry foyer extends through to the sun drenched open plan lounge and dining room. Adjoining fully equipped kitchen with gas hot plates, under bench wall oven, dishwasher, breakfast bar and additional filtered water tap.
3 bedrooms, 3 toilets and 2 bathrooms. Main bedroom features a walk in robe and full ensuite. Bedroom 2 has direct ensuite access to the 2nd bathroom and bedroom 3 has easy access to the 3rd toilet. Clever in design and layout throughout with loads of storage and cupboard space.
The outdoor entertaining deck extends seamlessly from the dining area via French doors and is partially covered for year round entertaining.
Ducted heating, split system cooling, quality blockout blinds,water tanks and security system are just some of the extras included. 6 star energy rating.For investors seeking a low maintenance investment, the potential return of this quality villa is $430-$450 per week.
Fabulous location with only a 10 minute walk to Yarraman Station, easy access to primary and secondary colleges and minutes to the entry of Eastlink and Monash freeways. It's right here that you get to live the dream!

Description:
FAMILY FRIENDLY AT ITS FINEST!
Wow! What a home. What an opportunity for young families.
Be captivated by this delightful family home situated in a quiet street just moments from Eastlink.
With instant street appeal the home sits commandingly on this spacious allotment of 649m2 approximately.
With wide street frontage the home has great appeal with its remote iron gate and picturesque iron fence.
Enter the home via the raised tiled patio and be impressed immediately by the immaculate presentation. High ceilings with ornamental cornices create an immediately stylish charisma to the home.
A tiled hallway with glistening polished floor boards throughout the bedrooms, kitchen and living areas adds further to the ambience within.
All bedrooms are super spacious with built in robes. The living areas comprise an elegant formal lounge which flows through to a very roomy dining/living area off a modernised kitchen.
The kitchen has a large window to the wonderful world of the large backyard ideal for the young family. Prepare meals whilst keeping a close eye on the children enjoying the open space to burn off energy.
Relax under the very large pergola the width of the home in all weather conditions.
The long driveway leads to a secure single carport behind a remote roll-a-door and leads to a very large double garage workshop with further shedding at the rear.
Extras are endless including ducted heating for winter warmth, an air conditioner in the dining area, security shutters on windows and terra cotta tiled roof!

Description:
Stylish Townhouse - 3 Bedrooms!
Located in central Dandenong in a convenient popular location, this spacious modern townhouse offers easy stylish living.
Offering large fully tiled area living with several lovely windows looking over the front garden area, separate tiled dining room which immediately adjoins the kitchen. Gas hot plates, underbench wall oven and a large walk in storage pantry. Downstairs laundry and toilet.
Upstairs features 3 spacious bedrooms with robes and a full ensuite bathroom to main bedroom. Separate family bathroom and additional separate toilet. The rear courtyard garden area and garage with additional carport is accessible via sliding glass doors off the meals area. Ducted heating throughout and split system air conditioning.
Located within walking distance to Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong Market, train station, buses and schools this townhouse is the epitome of convenience. Move in immediately or lease immediately with current income of $410pw upon settlement.
